relationships.description: Harry Potter is Dudley Dursley's cousin.
relationships.evidence: The figure in front was unmistakably his cousin, Dudley Dursley
Vernon Dursley, Harry’s uncle, suddenly spoke.
Aunt Petunia’s thin, horsey face now appeared beside Uncle Vernon’s

relationships.description: Harry fought off Dementors in Little Whinging.
relationships.evidence: Harry was sure that the cracking noise had been made by someone Apparating or Disapparating... Two dementors turned up

relationships.description: Harry cast a Patronus to repel Dementors.
relationships.evidence: EXPECTO PATRONUM! An enormous silver stag erupted from the tip of Harry’s wand

relationships.description: Mrs. Figg was tasked by Dumbledore to watch over Harry.
relationships.evidence: Dumbledore’s orders. I was to keep an eye on you but not say anything

relationships.description: Mundungus was supposed to be tailing Harry but abandoned his post.
relationships.evidence: Dementors attacking the boy on your watch!

relationships.description: Mundungus is a member of the Order.
relationships.evidence: It pays to have someone like Dung around, he hears things we don’t.

relationships.description: Sirius Black is currently living in his parents' house, serving as HQ.
relationships.evidence: This was my parents’ house... But I’m the last Black left, so it’s mine now.

relationships.description: The headquarters of the Order is at Grimmauld Place.
relationships.evidence: The headquarters of the Order of the Phoenix may be found at number twelve, Grimmauld Place, London.

relationships.description: Lupin is part of the Advance Guard and the Order.
relationships.evidence: Remus Lupin stood nearest to him... We’ve come to take you away.

relationships.description: Moody is part of the Advance Guard.
Tonks is part of the Advance Guard.
relationships.evidence: And this is Nymphadora — Don’t call me Nymphadora, Remus

relationships.description: Kingsley is part of the Advance Guard.
Kreacher is the house-elf of the Black family, serving Sirius.
relationships.evidence: Kreacher lives to serve the noble house of Black

relationships.description: Percy has been promoted to Junior Assistant to the Minister.
relationships.evidence: He came home and told us he’d been promoted... Junior Assistant to the Minister.

relationships.description: Percy is Ron's brother, though currently estranged.
relationships.evidence: Whatever you do, don’t mention Percy in front of Mum and Dad
